OL,6,FA motorist killed a pensioner in a car
OL,7,Fpark after being unable to see her due
OL,8,Fto the vehicle's steamed-up windows, a
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FMay Mustey, 45, hit Gwendoline Owen,
OL,12,F75, in the Waitrose car park in
OL,13,FMonmouth, south Wales, on the
OL,14,Fafternoon of 31 December 2022.
OL,16,Fheard Mustey's car windows were
OL,17,Fsteamed up but due to her
OL,18,F"impatience", she was driving with her
OL,19,Fhead stuck out of the window and
OL,20,Feyewitnesses watched her erratic
OL,21,Fdriving.
