OL,6,FAs she left the car park she struck
OL,7,FMrs Owen, who suffered fatal head
OL,8,Finjuries and died hours later in
OL,9,Fhospital, with her car.
OL,11,FJohn Ryan, prosecuting, told the court
OL,12,Fthe collision took place at around
OL,13,F4.15 pm on New Year's Eve as it was
OL,14,Fgetting dark.
OL,16,FMr Ryan said: "She started the vehicle
OL,17,Fand waited for a little bit for the
OL,18,Fheaters and air vents to clear the
OL,19,Fglass and said that she began to drive
OL,20,Fwhen she could see only through the
OL,21,Flower half of the windscreen.
