OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F467A1713031104
OL,3,CMotorist with steamed-up windows
OL,4,Ckilled pensioner in car park
OL,6,F"She also said that having completed a
OL,7,Fright-hand turn she realised that she
OL,8,Fhad no view through the glass.
OL,10,F"So she stopped her vehicle, lowered
OL,11,Fthe driver's side window and stretched
OL,12,Fher head outside of the vehicle to
OL,13,Fgive some forward view as she
OL,14,Frestarted her journey through the car
OL,15,Fpark and prepared to complete a second
OL,16,Fright-hand turn, which is where the
OL,17,Ffatal collision took place.
OL,19,F"She confirmed she did not lower the
OL,20,Fpassenger side window so effectively
OL,21,Fhad no left-hand view.
