OL,3,CMotorist with steamed-up windows
OL,4,Ckilled pensioner in car park
OL,6,F"She said she then heard a thump or
OL,7,Fbump noise from the front of her car
OL,8,Fand saw the top half of a figure
OL,9,Fcolliding with the front of her car
OL,10,Fand falling away.
OL,12,F"The prosecution's case is this,
OL,13,Fwhilst at that time, it was dark or
OL,14,Fdusk, the car park was well lit.
OL,16,F"Mrs Mustey chose to drive the vehicle
OL,17,Fknowing she had limited visibility by
OL,18,Fgiving insufficient time for her
OL,19,Fwindows to be demisted.
