OL,6,F"She also had her windscreen wipers
OL,7,Fset as an incorrect setting to
OL,8,Feffectively clear the rain from her
OL,9,Fwindscreen.
OL,11,F"Mrs Mustey cut the corner near the
OL,12,Fsupermarket entrance and drove harshly
OL,13,Fover an empty disabled parking space `
OL,14,Fan indicator of how little she could
OL,15,Fsee."
OL,17,FThe court heard Mrs Owen's husband was
OL,18,Fin poor health and living in a care
OL,19,Fhome and there were no other surviving
OL,20,Frelatives.
