OL,6,FAt a previous hearing Mustey, of
OL,7,FMaypole, Monmouth, pleaded guilty to a
OL,8,Fcharge of causing death by dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,FOwen Williams, defending, said Mustey
OL,12,Fhad written a "heartfelt and genuine
OL,13,Fletter of apology" to the family of
OL,14,FMrs Owen.
OL,16,FHe added: "There is a pre-sentence
OL,17,Freport and a number of character
OL,18,Freferences that provides full details
OL,19,Fof Mrs Mustey's life history and her
OL,20,Fpersonal circumstances.
