OL,6,F"There are a number of references from
OL,7,Ffriends and colleagues who highlight
OL,8,Fthe very positive features of their
OL,9,Fpersonality ` honest, generous and a
OL,10,Fcaring person, friend and colleague
OL,11,Fand also a devoted and loving mother
OL,12,Fand wife."
OL,14,FThe court heard Mustey had since lost
OL,15,Fher job as a teaching assistant in a
OL,16,Fschool.
OL,18,FJudge Paul Hobson imposed a 20-month
OL,19,Fprison sentence, suspended for 18
OL,20,Fmonths, and banned her from driving
OL,21,Ffor five years.
